Now, this is music.

00:24:31.236 --> 00:24:33.676 align:middle line:84%
(SINGING) I'm getting
bugged driving up and down

00:24:33.676 --> 00:24:35.140 align:middle line:90%
the same old strip.

00:24:35.140 --> 00:24:38.556 align:middle line:84%
I've gotta find a new place
where the kids are hip.

